    <p>When your LG dryer's gas valve fails, call (323) 990-7550 for same-day diagnosis and repair. Our technicians will assess your specific model, explain the exact costs upfront, and typically complete the repair the same day with OEM parts. We're available Monday through Saturday, 8am to 8pm, and waive our diagnostic fee when you proceed with the repair. No surprises, no inflated quotes — just straightforward gas valve replacement by licensed professionals who specialize in LG dryers.</p>
